Our test environment is fully isolated within VLAN 10.47.2.0/24 with no external connectivity. All package installations target our internal npm registry mirror at npm-detlab.internal.corp (10.47.2.15). Test containers are destroyed after each validation cycle. All telemetry streams to our SIEM at siem.internal.corp:514. Test payloads are instrumented to write only to /tmp/supply_chain_test_marker.log for detection validation.

